---
// Landing body, Arm A — adapted from context/raw/FAND_staged_facade/index.html
import SectionContext from "../SectionContext.astro";

const pathways = [
  {
    href: "/evidence/",
    label: "The Data",
    context: "200+ countries, 3,000+ counties, 75 years, one identity — see the roots.",
  },
  {
    href: "/framework/",
    label: "What We Measure",
    context:
      "The balance-sheet identity FAND uses to read a country like a company that answers to its owners.",
  },
  {
    href: "/methodology/",
    label: "Methods",
    context:
      "How each number earns its badge — Production, Experimental, or Prototype — and the audit trail behind it.",
  },
];
---

<section class="hero-video-stub" aria-labelledby="hero-video-heading">
  <h2 id="hero-video-heading" class="visually-hidden">Overview video</h2>
  <div class="hero-video-frame">
    <video class="hero-video" controls preload="metadata" playsinline>
      <source src="/video/FAND_TL1_Overview.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
      <p>
        Your browser can't play HTML5 video.
        <a href="/video/FAND_TL1_Overview.mp4">Download the MP4</a> (17 MB).
      </p>
    </video>
  </div>
  <p class="hero-video-caption">
    A five-minute walkthrough of the FAND framework at the country (TL1) scale.
  </p>
</section>

<p class="headline-stat">
  <span class="headline-stat-number">237</span>
  <span class="headline-stat-text">
    countries &mdash; one accounting crosstab, and a ledger the owners can
    finally read.
  </span>
</p>

<blockquote>
  <p>
    In the founders' usage, "wealth" still carried its older sense &mdash;
    <strong>weal</strong>, the flourishing of the commonweal (from
    <em>wele</em>, "well-being"). FAND writes that older sense as
    <strong>Welth</strong>: not just cash flow, but the organic,
    multi-dimensional condition of a people doing well.
  </p>
  <p>
    To protect that Welth, the Constitution built <strong>the Enumeration</strong>
    (Article I, &sect;2) &mdash; a literal ledger of consent, tying
    representation and taxation to the physical reality of the people. In
    1890 that tether snapped: the punch-card tabulator made data processing
    cheap, but the cost of quality control stayed fixed, so the accounts
    collapsed toward whatever a punch card could read. FAND is the
    correction &mdash; agentic AI is the first technology cheap enough to
    rebuild the full ledger, from the roots up.
  </p>
</blockquote>

<section class="pathway-cards" aria-label="Where to go next">
  <ul>
    {pathways.map((p) => (
      <li>
        <a class="pathway-card" href={p.href}>
          <h3>{p.label}</h3>
          <SectionContext>{p.context}</SectionContext>
        </a>
      </li>
    ))}
  </ul>
</section>
